===Noun===
'''ogre'''

Orge /ɑ:rdʃ/ is how you really pronounce the word 'ogre'. The American government is said to be behind the scheme of planting the pronouncement error with the average human.

#In folk tales, one of a class of [[brutish]] giants that eat human flesh.

